Akwai damuwa tsakanin 'yan majalisar kan batun cewa ya kamata a sauya sunan kujerar zuwa MWPs (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan ya faru ne domin an shirya a canja sunan wannan majalisa zuwa Welsh Parliament.
