Peter Jones ya 'ji haushi' bayan da Holly Willoughby ta fita daga kasuwancin fam miliyan 11
Shahararren dan wasan Dragons Den Peter Jones ya 'yi fushi' bayan da mai watsa shirye-shiryen fim Holly Willoughby ta bar £ 11m da kuma kasuwancinsa na rayuwa don kula da sabon haɗin kasuwanci tare da Marks and Spencer da ITV
Willoughby ba shi da lokacin yin aiki a kan kayan gida da kayan aiki na Truly.
An yi amfani da kasuwancin biyu a matsayin kayan aikin Goop Gwyneth Paltrow.
Wata mai shekara 37 da ke yin shirin nan This Morning ta yi amfani da dandalin sada zumunta na Instagram don sanar da cewa za ta yi murabus.
Ficewar Holly Willoughby daga Dragons' Den ya sa Peter Jones ya fusata sosai domin Holly ya bar kasuwancin kayan kwalliya wanda ya ba shi kuɗi da yawa a cikin ɗan gajeren lokaci - don mayar da hankali kan sabon haɗin gwiwa na kasuwanci tare da Marks & Spencer da ITV.
Wata majiya ta ce Jones ya "ji haushi" lokacin da wata sananniyar mai watsa shirye-shiryen ta amince da hakan a wani taron tattaunawa da aka yi a ranar Talata a babban ofishinsu a Marlow, Buckinghamshire, cewa sabon kasuwancinsa - wanda aka ce ya kai £1.5 miliyan - yana nufin cewa ba shi da lokacin da zai yi amfani da shi wajen sayar da kayan gida da sauran kayayyakin Truly.
An kwatanta wannan da dukiyar Gwyneth Paltrow ta Goop kuma an yi hasashen cewa zai iya ninka dukiyar Willoughby ta £11 million.
Lokacin da Willoughby, mai shekara 37, ya sanar a shafin Instagram cewa zai bar Truly, Jones ya bar Birtaniya don ya tafi gidansa na hutu.
Wani mai ba da rahoto ya ce: "Aikin Truly ya fi aikin da Holly take yi kyau.
Ya gina masa kasuwanci mai riba da zai iya ciyar da shi shekaru da yawa.
Abin da ya cim ma ya sa dukan waɗanda suka yi masa wannan aikin mamaki.
Babu wanda ya yarda da abin da ya faru a ranar Talata, ya kawo kusa da buɗewar kasuwanni.
Akwai wani kantin sayar da kayayyaki da aka buɗe a Marlow HQ da ke jiran a sayar da su".
Masu ruwa da tsaki sun ce fitowar wani mai gabatar da shirin na This Morning, wanda ya kasance daya daga cikin manyan masu saka jari a Burtaniya, zai iya yin illa ga ayyukan shagon da ke samar da kayayyaki da dama da suka hada da kayan abinci da kayan kwalliya da kayan gida, tare da jinkirin bude shagon.
Kuma yana iya zama ƙarshen dangantaka mai daɗewa.
Mahaifin 'ya'ya uku Willoughby da matarsa Dan Baldwin sun kasance tare da Jones da matarsa Tara Capp na shekaru goma.
Willoughby ya fara kasuwancin Truly tare da Capp a shekara ta 2016 kuma Jones, mai shekaru 52, ya shiga cikin watan Maris.
Wannan rukunin da Jones suna da kashi 40 cikin ɗari na tallace - tallace na Baldwin.
Willoughby ya zama wakilin talla na M&S kuma ya maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin mai gabatar da shirin ITV na I'm A Celebrity.
"Ba za mu iya tattauna batun kasuwanci ba", in ji wani mai magana da ya zo kusa da Jones a daren jiya.
