Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump zai fara zabensa na farko a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan yana ɗaya daga cikin tarurruka biyar da Trump ya shirya a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya haɗa da tarurrukan da ke cikin yankuna da ke da yawan jama'a kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da aka yi tsammanin za a kammala zaben don cike kujerun da ke Kotun Koli, Mista Trump ya yi niyyar ƙara yawan goyon baya ga zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, inda 'yan Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rasa shugabancin majalisar a lokacin zaben na Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne taron Trump a West Virginia a yau da dare kuma ta yaya za ku iya shiga yanar gizo?
An dakatar da taron Trump a West Virginia da karfe 7 na yammacin ET a daren yau, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump na West Virginia a YouTube ta hanyar watsa shirye-shirye kai tsaye.
Ana sa ran Trump zai yi magana a kotun koli a wannan makon a kan Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ake zargi da laifin yin lalata da mace mai ciki, yayin da aka dakatar da zaben tabbatar da hakan a wannan makon a binciken da FBI ke yi.
Amma, ainihin aikin taron shi ne ya shirya 'yan Republican don zaɓen Nuwamba da ke tafe.
Don haka, yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump na wannan makon ya ta'allaka ne kan "ba wa 'yan Republican masu son ci gaba da goyon baya damar kare da kuma karfafa kujerun da suke da su a Majalisar Dattawa da Majalisar Wakilai", a cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
"Shugabannin Majalisa sun yi wa shugaban kasa takunkumi a kan tafiye-tafiye da yawa a lokacin da ake shiga cikin mawuyacin lokaci don zaɓen", in ji wani mai magana da yawun kamfen din Trump wanda ya ƙi ya ambaci sunan kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
An shirya taron a filin wasan Wesbanco Arena da ke Wheeling, kuma an yi hasashen taron na yau zai kawo masu goyon baya daga " Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma masu sauraro da yawa a tashoshin rediyo na Pittsburgh, " in ji West Virginia Metro News.
Ranar Asabar za ta kasance ranar Talata ta biyu a watan da Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia, duk da cewa wannan jihar ta lashe fiye da kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un da aka kada a zaben 2016.
Mr Trump na kokarin tallafawa dan takarar Sanata Patrick Morrisey na Republican daga West Virginia, wanda ya yi watsi da zaben.
"Ba zai yi kyau ba idan shugaban ya zo ya taimaka wa Mr. Morrissey wajen samun kuri'un da zai jefa masa", in ji Simon Haeder, farfesa a fannin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, in ji kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
