Jami'an tsaron Koriya ta Arewa sun shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa takunkumin ya kara sanya Amurka cikin halin da ba za ta iya yin watsi da makaman nukiliyarta ba.
Ri Yong Ho ya gaya wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "matakai masu kyau" a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin nukiliya, lalata cibiyar gwajin nukiliya da kuma dakatar da gina tashoshin nukiliya da kayan aiki.
"Duk da haka, ba mu ga wani martani daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
