Ƙarƙashin cutar HIV da Aids: Kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton kashi 14 cikin 100 na sabbin masu kamuwa da cutar
China ta ba da rahoton ƙaruwar yawan mutanen da ke rayuwa da cutar HIV da AIDS da kashi 14 cikin ɗari.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne cutar ta shafa a ƙasar, in ji wani babban jami'in kiwon lafiya.
An kama kusan 40,000 da aka kashe a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai.
Yawancin mutane da suka yi hakan sun yi hakan ne ta hanyar yin hira, ba kamar yadda na yi a dā ba.
A dā, ana yaɗuwar cutar ƙanjamau a ƙasar Sin ta wurin yin amfani da jini.
Amma yanzu an rage yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar ta HIV a wannan hanyar zuwa kusan sifili, in ji ma'aikatan lafiya da ke taron a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, idan aka gwada da na shekarun baya, adadin mutanen da suke da cutar HIV da Aids a ƙasar Sin ya ƙaru da 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i ta zama babbar matsala a kasar Sin inda yawanci 'yan luwadi da 'yan madigo suke.
An haramta luwadi a China a shekara ta 1997, amma an ce zaluntar LGBT ta fi tsanani.
Saboda wannan al'ada da aka sani, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 na maza da suke da dangantaka da maza sun yi jima'i da mata.
Yawancin irin wannan ɓarnawar ta taso ne saboda rashin cikakkiyar dangantaka.
A shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin ƙasar Sin ta yi alkawarin ba dukan 'yan ƙasar rigakafin cutar ƙanjamau don magance cutar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa labarin da aka fitar game da 'yan majalisar GOP' na yada 'karya mai haɗari' da 'labari na karya'
A ranar Asabar ne, 'yar majalisar wakilai ta Amurka Maxine Waters ta yi watsi da zargin da ake yi cewa wani a ma'aikatarta ya saka wasu bayanai na 'yan Republican guda uku a shafinta na Wikipedia.
Dan takarar Democrat na Los Angeles ya ce " yan adawa na dama" ne suka kirkiro wannan bidiyon, tare da wasu shafukan yanar gizo.
"Maƙaryaci, ƙarya ce, ƙarya ce ta ɓoye", in ji Waters a cikin wani sakon Twitter.
An ba da rahoton cewa jawabin da aka watsa ya ƙunshi adireshin gida da lambar waya na U. S. Sens. Lindsey Graham na South Carolina, Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka biyu daga Utah.
Labarin ya bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani mutum da ba a san ko shi waye ba ya wallafa a fadar Capitol Hill a lokacin da ake sauraron shari'ar da ake yi wa dan takarar da aka zaɓa a kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, a kotun da ke Washington.
Labarin ya bazu bayan da sanatoci uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh shari'a.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ba da rahoton cewa adireshin IP ɗin da ke bayyana mai aikawa ya kasance yana da alaka da ofishin Waters kuma ya ba da labarin ga ma'aikacin Waters, in ji Hill.
"Wannan zato marar tushe, ya yi daidai da rashin gaskiya, kuma ya sa ya zama ƙarya", in ji Waters.
"Bawana - wanda ka shirya da alamu, da al'ajabai, da kuma labaru na yaudara - ba da gaske ya ba da labarin wannan.
"Wannan hasashe marar tushe ya nuna cewa ƙarya ce kuma ba a cika gaskatawa ba.
Bayanin Waters ya zama abin takaici da yawa a kan layi, ciki har da jaridar White House Ari Fleischer.
Fleischer ya rubuta: "Wannan ƙin yana da ban haushi.
"Wannan yana nufin cewa ba shi da zuciyar zama memba na Ƙungiyar Shari'a.
Idan aka yi wa mutum horo don wani abin da bai yi ba, kada ya yi fushi.
Bai kamata ya yi fushi don ya kāre kansa ba.
Bai kamata ta tambayi mai zargin ba.
Amma ya kamata ya kasance da tawali'u da kuma haƙuri".
Fleischer yana kokarin gwada fushin Waters da na 'yan Democrat da suka yi wa Alkalin Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi zargin cewa ya yi fushi a lokacin da ake sauraron shari'ar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar Republican wanda ya yi kira da a cire Waters daga kujerar shugaban kasa a zaben tsakiyar shekara, ya yi tsokaci a shafinsa na Twitter.
"Wannan babban abu ne idan gaskiya ne", in ji wani mai amfani da Twitter.
A cikin jawabinsa, Waters ya ce ofishin sa ya "yi kira ga duk wanda ya shafi wannan shari'ar da kuma duk wanda ke da alhakin aikata wannan laifi.
"Za mu tabbata cewa an kama masu laifi", in ji shi, "kuma za a hukunta su saboda ayyukansu na lalata da kuma yi wa kowa lahani tare da ma'aikatan su".
