Mene ne Global Citizen Festival kuma shin ya yi wani abu game da rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar a New York za a yi bikin Global Citizen Festival, wanda ake yi kowace shekara kuma masu zane -zane daga wurare dabam dabam suke halarta, kuma za a yi wa'azi a kan batun nan mai muhimmanci; kawar da talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen zai jawo dubun dubatan mutane zuwa babban filin shakatawa na Central Park ba kawai don sauraron waƙoƙin mawaƙa kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don wayar da kan jama'a game da shirin kiɗa na duniya wanda zai kawo ƙarshen zalunci a duniya kafin 2030.
An fara bikin Global Citizen Festival a shekara ta 2012 a matsayin ci gaba da Global Poverty Project, wani shiri na duniya da ke fatan magance talauci ta hanyar haɓaka yawan jama'a da ke cikin yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta (sai dai idan kuna son siyan tikiti na VIP), masu sha'awar za su kammala wasu ayyukan da aka tsara, ko "aiki" kamar su ba da kai ga aikin, aikawa da shugaban kasa, yin kira ko kuma wani aikin da zai kawo ƙarshen wannan aikin.
Bayan shekara 12 da aka kafa wannan shiri, shin ya cim ma wani abu?
