Mickelson ya yi watsi da wasan da ya yi a gasar Ryder a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai yi suna a ranar Lahadi a wasan sa na 47 a gasar Ryder Cup, amma dole ne ya yi kokari sosai don ya guji yin rashin nasara.
Mickelson, wanda ya yi wasa a shekara ta 12 a gasar, ya yi wasa a wasan na huɗu da na huɗu na ranar Asabar tare da kocinsa Jim Furyk.
A lokacin da yake tsakiyar wasan, kamar yadda yake a lokacin da yake tafiya a Amurka, wannan mai nasara sau hudu ya raba ranarsa tsakanin kasancewa mai farin ciki da kuma aiki a kan tawagarsa don magance matsalolin da ke damun sa.
Ba tare da wani ƙwararren direba ba ko kuma mafi kyawun ƙwarewarsa, ɗan wasan mai shekara 48 ba zai iya yin wasa a filin Le Golf National ba, inda tsawon filin wasa yake da wuyar shawo kan ciwon ciki da ke fitowa daga ƙashin baya.
Kuma idan tsayin filin ba zai zama matsala ba, Mickelson, a wasansa na tara a ranar Lahadi ya yi karo da zakaran British Open Francesco Molinari, wanda ya yi aiki tare da ƙwararren mai horarwa Tommy Fleetwood don lashe wasanni 4 da ya yi a wannan makon.
Idan 'yan wasan Amirka, waɗanda suka yi nasara sau huɗu a wasan farko da suka yi, suka ci gaba da wasa, to wasan Mickelson zai zama na ƙuruciya.
Furyk ya amince da mutumin sosai, amma ba ya son ya ƙara ba da bayani.
"Ta san yadda za ta yi aikin yau, ta dan dan yi min sumba ta ce za ta shirya gobe", in ji Furyk.
"Yana da ra'ayin kansa.
Yana daya daga cikin manyan masu neman shiga cikin Hall of Famer kuma ya yi aiki mai yawa don wannan rukunin a baya, har ma a wannan makon.
Ban taɓa tunanin cewa zai yi wanka sau biyu ba.
Ba mu yi haka a cikin zuciyarmu ba, sai dai a cikinku.
Yana son ya halarci taro kamar yadda kowa yake so ya yi".
Mickelson ya zarce Faldo a matsayin dan wasan da ya fi kowa a gasar cin kofin Ryder da za a yi a ranar Lahadi.
Wannan zai zama ƙarshen wasan da ya lashe Ryder Cup, wanda ba zai taɓa kai na ƙwallo ba.
Mickelson ya ci nasara sau 18, ya ci nasara sau 20 kuma ya yi nasara, duk da cewa Furyk ya ce kasancewar sa ya kawo kyakkyawan sakamako ga kungiyar.
"Yana da ban dariya, yana da ban dariya, yana da ban dariya, yana da ban dariya, kuma yana da kyau a cikin ɗakin", in ji ta.
"Ina fata cewa matasa da suke wasa suna jin daɗin wannan, kamar yadda na ji daɗin wannan makon, wanda ya kasance mai ban sha'awa.
Ya fi ni a yalwace".
Shugaban Turai Thomas Bjorn ya san cewa za a iya rasa sanannen shugabancinsa
Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin na Turai, ya sani daga abin da ya gani da kuma abin da ya faru cewa ya fi shahara a cikin wasan karshe na Ryder Cup zai iya zama mai ban tsoro.
Dan wasan Danish ya fara fitowa a wasan 1997 a Valderrama, inda mai kula da 'yan wasan Seve Ballesteros ya ci Amurka da kwallaye 5 amma a ƙarshe ya gama kusan kwallaye 141⁄2-131⁄2.
"A koyaushe kuna tuna cewa mun kasance a gaba a filin Valderrama; mun kasance a gaba a Brookline, inda muka yi nasara, kuma a Valderrama, inda muka yi nasara", in ji Bjorn, wanda aka nuna a hoton, bayan kallon Class of 2018 ya lashe 5-3 a ranar Juma'a da kuma na jiya da kuma 10-6 a Le Golf National.
Saboda haka, abubuwan da suka faru a baya sun nuna cewa wannan labarin ba zai ƙare ba.
Ka yi ƙoƙari sosai don ka kasance da ƙarfin yin abin da za ka yi gobe.
Ka yi abin da za ka iya.
Ba za ka iya magance matsalar ba sai ka yi abin da ake bukata.
A wajen tseren nan kuma, ba ma wasa da kome, sai dai dai na wahayi.
Kamar yadda nake yawan cewa, ina mai da hankali ne kawai ga 'yan wasa 12 da ke jam'iyyarmu, amma mun san waɗanda suke jam'iyyarmu - 'yan wasa mafi iko a duniya".
Da yake farin ciki da yadda 'yan wasansa suka yi wasa a filin wasa mai cike da damuwa, Bjorn ya kara da cewa: "Ba zan iya yin wasa ba tare da na shirya ba.
Gobe ne ranar da za ka sadu da dabbar.
Gobe za a yi bikin ɗaurin aure, kuma wannan biki ne na musamman.
