Ronaldo ya yi zargin cewa an yi masa fyade a lokacin da ake shirin kai karar jaridun Jamus zuwa kotu
Cristiano Ronaldo ya ce laifin da ake tuhumarsa da shi na yin "abin da ba daidai ba" ne, kuma "wasu mutane suna son su yi wa kansu laifi" ta wurin yin amfani da sunansa.
Lauyanta suna shirin kai ƙarar jaridar Der Spiegel ta Jamus, wadda ta wallafa wannan labari mai ban tsoro.
An dai zargi dan wasan na Juventus da laifin yin lalata da wata 'yar Amurka Kathryn Mayorga a wani otal a Las Vegas a shekarar 2009.
An ce bayan haka ta biya shi dala 375,000 don ta ba da labarin, in ji jaridar Der Spiegel a ranar Jumma'a.
A cikin wani jawabi da ya wallafa a shafinsa na Instagram wanda ya ga mutane miliyan 142 bayan wannan labarin, Ronaldo, mai shekara 33, ya musanta zargin da ake yi masa kuma ya kira shi "ƙarya".
"A'a, a'a, a'a, ba zan yi farin ciki ba.
"Babu wani abu da za a ce a yau, labari ne kawai", in ji ɗan wasan da ya ci kyautar Ballon d'Or sau biyar, yana kallon kyamarar.
"Suna son su kira ni da sunana.
Hakan yana faruwa.
Suna son a san sunana, amma ba su san ni ba.
"Ni mutum ne mai farin ciki da kuma lafiya", in ji shi, yana murmushi.
Masu gabatar da kara na Ronaldo sun yi niyyar kai karar jaridar Der Spiegel kan wannan zargi, wanda suka ce "yana ba da labarin da ba shi da tushe game da wani mutum", in ji kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
Lauyanmu, Christian Schertz, ya ce lauyan zai nemi a ba shi fansa bisa tuhumar da aka yi masa na "ɓata 'yan Adam a ɓangarori dabam dabam na doka, wanda ya zama ɗaya cikin laifuffukan haƙƙin ɗan adam da aka fi fuskanta a shekarun baya - bayan nan".
Wannan labarin ya faru ne a watan Yuni na shekara ta 2009 a wani ɗakin da ke Palms Hotel da Casino a Las Vegas.
Bayan sun hadu a gidan giya, Ronaldo da Mayorga sun koma gidan yarinyar, inda aka yi zargin cewa ya yi mata fyade a baya, a cewar takardun da aka shigar a Kotun Gundumar Clark da ke Nevada.
Mayorga ya ce Ronaldo ya fadi a kan gwiwoyi bayan wannan lamarin kuma ya ce ya zama "99 percent" "mai lafiya" wanda ya rage kawai "1 percent"
