Wani jami'i daga jihar Tennessee ya sanar da Chris Harris na WSMV a Nashville, Tennessee, cewa Abercrombie ya tafi don ya yi aiki a Cibiyar Kiwon Lafiya ta Vanderbilt.
Harris ya kara da cewa "babu wani tabbaci na ainihin nau'in da girman raunin da aka samu" kuma jihar Tennessee ta yi kokarin gano lokacin da raunin ya faru.
Abercrombie, ɗan wasan ƙwallon ƙafa na shekara ta biyu a makarantar, ya fara wasa da Tennessee State bayan ya koma daga Illinois.
