Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a ƙasar Indonesia
Mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar ƙasar da kuma ambaliyar ruwa da ta faru a birnin Palu a ranar Jumma'a, in ji hukuma, kuma ba a iya kirga adadin mutanen da suka mutu ba.
A lokacin da aka halaka tashoshin, masu aikin agaji ba su iya samun saƙo daga Donggala ba, wato, yankin da ke arewacin Palu da ke kusa da inda girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta faru.
A Palu, an yi wa mutane fiye da 16,000 jinya a lokacin bala'in.
Ga wasu bayanai game da yankunan Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi.
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Central Sulawesi, wanda ke kan iyaka na yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda ke da mazaunan kusan 379,800 a shekara ta 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da ambaliyar ruwa suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40 da samun 'yancin kai.
Donggala wani yanki ne mai nisan kilomita 300 da ke gabashin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Garin da ke da ofisoshin gwamnatin lardin yana da mazaunan 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan ayyukan da ke samar da tattalin arzikin lardin Central Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Donggala.
Ana kuma haƙa ma'adanai a wannan lardin, amma ana yawan haƙa ma'adanai a yankin Morowali, a gaɓar tekun Sulawesi.
Garin Palu da Donggala sun fuskanci girgizar ƙasa da ambaliyar ruwa a wurare da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, in ji Hukumar Kula da Bala'o'i ta Indonesiya.
A shekara ta 1938, ambaliyar ruwa ta kashe mutane 200 kuma ta rushe ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996, wata ambaliyar ruwa ta rufe Donggala, inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin girgizar kasa na Pacific Ring of Fire kuma tana yawan fuskantar girgizar ƙasa.
Ga jerin girgizar ƙasa da kuma manyan guguwar ruwa da suka faru a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo a lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da ambaliyar ruwa da ta shafi kasashe 14, ta kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, mafi yawansu a yankin Aceh.
2005: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Afrilu da farkon Satumba.
Dubban mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da gaɓar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afka wa kudancin Java, babban tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta jawo igiyar ruwa a gefen kudu, ta kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: An yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.6 a Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa da ta kai ƙarfin ƙarfinta 7.5 ta girgiza tsibirin Mentawai kusa da Sumatra, ta jawo raƙuman ruwa da suka kai tsawon ƙafa 10, kuma suka halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma suka kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani karamin girgizar kasa ya afka yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, inda ya haifar da lalacewa da damuwa yayin da aka tuna da bala'in girgizar kasa da ambaliyar ruwa a shekara ta 2004.
Babu ruwan sama a wannan lokacin, amma mutane fiye da ɗari sun mutu sanadiyyar faɗuwar.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin gaske ta afka wa Lombok, babban birnin yawon buɗe ido na ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, yawancinsu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasar ta hallaka gidaje da yawa kuma ta sa dubban mutane da suka zo daga wasu ƙasashe suka rasa gidajensu.
