Masu gabatar da kara na gwamnati a kotu suna neman a yanke wa wanda ake zargi da kai hari a birnin New York hukuncin kisa
A New York City, masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun bukaci a yanke wa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da kai hari a Birnin New York inda mutane takwas suka mutu - wanda ba a taɓa yin irin wannan shari'ar ba a cikin wannan ƙasar tun lokacin da aka yi wannan shari'ar a 1953.
Saipov, ɗan shekara 30, an ce ya yi amfani da motar Home Depot wajen yin wannan haɗari a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya kashe mutane masu hawan keke a lokacin bazara.
Don a yanke masa hukuncin kisa, lauyoyi na bukatar su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas a "wurin da aka yi" kuma ya raunata mutane takwas a "wurin da aka yi", a cewar sanarwar neman hukuncin kisa da aka shigar a Kudancin Gundumar New York.
Dukkanin tuhumar da aka yi wa mai laifin hukuncin kisa ne, kamar yadda kotun ta ce.
Bayan makonni da suka gabata bayan wannan hadarin, wani alƙali ya sami Saipov da laifin 22 wanda ya hada da kisan kai takwas da aka yi wa sa kai, wanda ake amfani da shi sau da yawa a matsayin mai kare gwamnati a cikin shari'ar da ba ta dace ba, da kuma laifin lalata motoci.
Wannan harin ya bukaci "tsara da kuma shiri na dogon lokaci", in ji mai gabatar da kara, wanda ya kwatanta Saipov da "mai zafin hali, marar tausayi, kuma mai nuna son kai".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya zama sanadin rauni, tashin hankali, da kuma asarar dangi da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji sanarwar.
Biyar daga cikin waɗanda aka yi wa addu'a baƙi ne daga ƙasar Argentina.
Shekara goma ke nan da Kotun Kudancin New York ta yanke hukuncin kisa na ƙarshe.
Babban mai gabatar da kara a lokacin, Khalid Barnes, an same shi da laifin kashe dillalan miyagun kwayoyi amma an yanke masa hukuncin kisa a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekara ta 1953 ne aka yanke wa Julius da Ethel Rosenberg hukuncin kisa a wani shari'ar da aka yi a New York, kuma an yanke wa ma'auratan hukuncin kisa domin sun yi makirci a lokacin Yaƙin Cacar Baki da Soviet a shekara biyu da ta shige.
An kashe su a cikin kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, wani mazaunin Uzbekistan, bai nuna nadama ba a cikin watanni bayan harin, in ji takardun kotu.
Ya gaya wa masu bincike cewa ya yi farin ciki da abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya shaida wa masu gabatar da kara cewa an yi masa kisan ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a kan wayar salula, a cewar bayanan shari'a.
Ya kuma nemi a saka masa tutar ISIS a asibitin da yake, in ji 'yan sanda.
Mutumin ya musanta dukan tuhume-tuhume 22 da aka yi masa.
David Patton, ɗaya daga cikin lauyoyin da suka wakilci Saipov, ya ce "ba su yi ba'a ba" game da hukuncin da aka yanke.
"Muna tunanin cewa neman hukuncin kisa a maimakon a yarda da laifin da ake da shi da kuma yanke hukuncin kisa zai kara daɗa wa waɗanda abin ya shafa wahala", in ji Paton.
Da farko lauyoyin Saipov sun tambayi lauyoyin ƙasar ko suna son a ba su hukuncin kisa.
